{"sequence":40,"timestamp":"2026-04-16T05:31:08.864122376Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-2088a645","body":"finding_summary: `BrMutationAdapter::sync_import()` only checks the adapter's in-memory dirty flag, so every fresh adapter instance is treated as clean even after a prior process crashed with unflushed `br` state. `BrMutationAdapter::new()` / `with_adapter()` always initialize `has_unsync_mutations` to `false` (src/adapters/br_process.rs:496-516), and `sync_import()` relies exclusively on `ensure_synced()` before running `br sync --import-only` (src/adapters/br_process.rs:529-543, 713-724). That means the documented recovery flow after `git pull` / failed-run restart can still import upstream JSONL over stale local mutations, which defeats the safety guarantee this bead is adding. severity: high. affected_files: src/adapters/br_process.rs. remediation_hint: persist or reconstruct pending-mutation state across restarts before allowing `sync_import()`, or narrow the API so import is rejected unless the caller has independently proven the workspace is clean.","dedup_key":"808dab18e794994bfbed698526a596c3561621ec29370f1861e8b2de5d54460d","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260416043549","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":41,"timestamp":"2026-04-16T05:31:08.873831816Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-67d5a423","body":"Missing test for `BrMutationAdapter::sync_import()` refusing to run when the adapter has pending (dirty) mutations. The doc comments and `ensure_synced` guard in `sync_import()` codify this as a key safety invariant, but no test exercises this rejection path. Add a test in `src/adapters/br_process.rs` that: (1) makes a mutation to set the dirty flag, (2) calls `sync_import()`, (3) asserts the call returns an error about pending mutations, and (4) verifies no subprocess was actually invoked via the command log.","dedup_key":"7838f3a6b531ab246bc219c895c2931c5fdd1ac1d485385b8d3127a12413d9f0","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"claude","model_id":"claude-opus-4-6-max","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260416043549","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
